Description: Choose which of the two photos is more complex
Answer.criteria: It's a bit hard to explain, but I think the simplest way to look at it is how many "layers" there were to the image.  Some felt almost blank, a clear sky with barely a wisp of a cloud, which I considered to be less complex than ones with one or two clouds.  It got a little more difficult when comparing images that had numerous clouds versus images that had large, connected ones that took up most of the space.  In cases where it was one large cloud with a mostly uniform color I considered that somewhat simple, while the large, interconnected clouds that had different shades within them from catching the light in different ways I considered to be the most complex images of all.
